column16: Casper Wells singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mike Trout.   Jesus Montero scores.    Michael Saunders scores.    Trayvon Robinson to 3rd.    Casper Wells to 2nd on the throw.
Dustin Ackley singles on a line drive to left fielder Mike Trout.
Carlos Triunfel lines out to right fielder Mark Trumbo.
Adrian Beltre grounds out, second baseman Howard Kendrick to first baseman Mark Trumbo.   Josh Hamilton to 2nd.
Josh Hamilton singles on a ground ball to third baseman Alberto Callaspo.
Michael Saunders singles on a ground ball to second baseman Howard Kendrick.
Justin Smoak flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.
John Jaso flies out to left fielder Vernon Wells.
A.  J.   Pierzynski hits a ground-rule double (16) on a fly ball to right field.   Alex Rios to 3rd.
Mike Moustakas flies out to right fielder Torii Hunter.
Alex Gordon grounds out, second baseman Howard Kendrick to first baseman Albert Pujols.   Alcides Escobar to 2nd.
Brandon Hicks flies out to right fielder Kole Calhoun.
Josh Reddick pops out to second baseman Howard Kendrick.
Coco Crisp grounds out, pitcher Nick Maronde to first baseman Kendrys Morales.
Cliff Pennington flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.
Stephen Drew out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Vernon Wells.   Josh Donaldson scores.
George Kottaras walks.   Brandon Moss to 2nd.
Brandon Moss singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mike Trout, deflected by shortstop Erick Aybar.
Carlos Peguero called out on strikes.
